data.description: Colonial-style two-story, 5-bed, 3-bath home in Foster Village. Offers a ground-level bedroom with full bath, versatile dining room, and expansive open living area. Updated with stainless steel appliances, custom kitchen cabinetry, granite countertops, vinyl flooring, and a sunroom overlooking the pool and backyard. Primary suite includes a spa-like tub, separate shower, dual sinks, and walk-in closets. Multiple spaces for entertaining with in-ground pool, spa, and  Dog run in the yard. New HVAC downstairs (2021). Conveniently positioned near Cross Timbers Park for relaxation and close proximity to schools.
